In sit amet arcu imperdiet risus egestas volutpat. Ut sed nisi non quam.

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Bordeaux custom list styles Default list style Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu. 				<title>Sample Page</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/sample-page/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 27 Jun 2011 08:20:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=2</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

<blockquote>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>

...or something like this:

<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>

As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!]]></content:encoded>

	<item>
				<title>Reservations</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/reservations/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 07:40:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=147</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Things to know, before you make your reservation</h2>
In sed odio libero, vitae elementum urna. Vestibulum et ligula sed lectus blandit pretium in non metus. Donec dapibus, ipsum vel vehicula tempor, purus urna vestibulum mi, eu tempor elit turpis vitae enim. Duis porttitor mi sed nisi rhoncus at porta tellus sagittis. &lt;br/&gt;--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

Version 1.3 is available &lt;strong&gt;(August 26)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt; * Menu cards improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; * Now you can order all categories and subcategories in the menu card, by just dragging &amp;amp; droping them in the new wp-admin section – Bordeaux Menu Category Order&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; * Now you are able to order all items in menu card, just type the item number in the Attributes fiel by adding a new menu card post. If you don’t see a Attributes box, click on “Screen options” and check Attributes. After that you will be able to order the items&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;br/&gt;--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

Version 1.0.8 is available &lt;strong&gt;(August 10)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt; * Menu cards improvements now you can open a specific page in menu card – see more in demo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; * Opportunity to add a full day in reservation calendar.&lt;/li&gt;

<h3>Selection title Headding</h3>
Proin egestas iaculis enim, ullamcorper porttitor justo placerat quis. Sed adipiscing ipsum sed leo molestie auctor. Nam ullamcorper porta lorem ut adipiscing.
<ul>
	<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
	<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
	<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
	<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
</ul>
In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Nunc ipsum neque, vulputate nec laoreet at, venenatis at est. Donec et mauris quis tellus pharetra tempor nec eget diam. Nulla sapien diam, tincidunt quis laoreet non, dictum sit amet odio. Quisque et dui ut enim lobortis commodo. Nam at velit a purus semper sollicitudin ut quis felis.

Phasellus ultricies arcu eleifend urna vehicula dignissim nec at urna. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Ut vehi cula, risus in bibendum luctus, ligula lacus aliquet diam, et varius dui arcu id lacus.

Donec a blandit sem. Integer et dui vitae lorem sollicitudin ultrices eu eget lorem. Phasellus imperdiet massa sed metus hendrerit nec interdum diam molestie. Pellentesque et accumsan mi. Integer sit amet tellus at elit laoreet.

	<item>
				<title>Buttons</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/buttons/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 09:38:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=261</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3><a href="#">Bordeaux custom button styles</a></h3>
<h4>Small buttons</h4>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-default btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-grey btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-red btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-yellow btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-green btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-color-blue btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-1 btn-1-disabled btn-1-align-left"><span>Sample of a shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<div class="clear"></div>

					
													<p>Create small sized button with following shortcode. If size is not defined, then default is small.</p>
													
													<code>[button size="small"]<br />&emsp;...<br />[/button]</code>
													
													<p>You can choose between 5 different colors - <b>grey</b>, <b>red</b>, <b>yellow</b>, <b>green</b> and <b>blue</b>.</p>
													
													<p>Alternatively, you can choose not to add color, in whitch case button will be default white. Also, you can make button appear disabled, by adding <b>color="disabled"</b> styling.</p>
													
													<code>[button size="small" color="blue"]<br />&emsp;...<br />[/button]</code>
												
	<p>You can also add link to the button</p>
													
													<code>[button size="small" link="http://www.orange-themes.com"]<br />&emsp;...<br />[/button]</code>
								
													<p>There is also a possibility to align your button to <b>left</b> or <b>right</b> side.</p>
													
													<code>[button size="small" color="blue" align="left"]<br />&emsp;...<br />[/button]</code>
												
													<h4>Big buttons</h4>

													<p><a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-default btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-grey btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-red btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-yellow btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-green btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-color-blue btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<a href="#" class="btn-2 btn-2-disabled btn-2-align-left"><span>Sample of a big shortcode button</span></a>
													
													<div class="clear"></div>

													
													<code>[button size="big" color="blue" align="left"]<br />&emsp;...<br />[/button]</code>
													]]></content:encoded>

	<item>
				<title>Lists</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/lists/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 09:40:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=268</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[													<h3><a href="#">Bordeaux custom list styles</a></h3>

													<h4>Default list style</h4>

													<ul>
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create default styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>
													
													<h4>Light list style</h4>
													
													<ul class="light">
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create light styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list style="light"]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>
													
													<h4>Checkmark list style</h4>
													
													<ul class="checkmark">
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create checkmark styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list style="checkmark"]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>
													
													<h4>Cross list style</h4>
													
													<ul class="cross">
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create cross styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list style="cross"]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>
													
													<h4>Block list style</h4>
													
													<ul class="block">
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create block styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list style="block"]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>
													
													<h4>Star list style</h4>
													
													<ul class="star">
														<li>Mauris elit erat, laoreet ac posuere eget, blandit at nunc fusce non orci eu arcu.</li>
														<li>Vestibulum vitae justo nisi, nec pharetra ipsum fusce lobortis.</li>
														<li>Donec ornare dapibus ante ut porttitor nam sit amet senttima nunc ornare erat imperdiet.</li>
														<li>Aliquam vestibulum condimentum leo, vel porta sapien atsu ultricies vel.</li>
													</ul>
													
													<p>You can create star styled lists with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[list style="star"]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />&emsp;[item]...[/item]<br />[/list]</code>

	<item>
				<title>Menu Card Shortcodes</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/menu-card-shortcodes/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 09:41:09 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=270</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3><a href="#">Bordeaux custom wrapper styles</a></h3>
<h4>Ingredients wrapper style</h4>
<div class="ingredients-wrapper">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<div class="ingredients">
<ul>
	<li>1/2 cup oat bran</li>
	<li>1 cup wheat bran</li>
	<li>1/2 cup sour cream</li>
	<li>1/2 cup milk</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>
You can dashed box quote with following shortcode:

<code>[ingredients title="Ingredients"]
&lt;ul&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup oat bran&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;1 cup wheat bran&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup sour cream&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup milk&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;/ul&gt;
[/ingredients]
</code>


<h4>Directions wrapper style</h4>
<div class="directions-wrapper">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ol>
	<li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec leo mauris, aliquam bibendum tincidunt nec.</li>
	<li>Mauris eu massa vel massa tincidunt feugiat quis a enim.</li>
	<li>Morbi felis elit, varius nec volutpat at, iaculis at mauris. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Quisque fermentum felis scelerisque augue bibendum eu tincidunt eros accumsan.</li>
</ol>
</div>
<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>
You can dashed box quote with following shortcode:

<code>[directions title="Directions"]
&lt;ol&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec leo mauris, aliquam bibendum tincidunt nec.&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;Mauris eu massa vel massa tincidunt feugiat quis a enim.&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;li&gt;Morbi felis elit, varius nec volutpat at, iaculis at mauris. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Quisque fermentum felis scelerisque augue bibendum eu tincidunt eros accumsan.&lt;/li&gt;<br/>
&lt;/ol&gt;
[/directions]
</code>
]]></content:encoded>

				<title>Quote </title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/quote/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 09:41:27 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=272</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[													<h3><a href="#">Bordeaux custom quote styles</a></h3>

													<h4>Default quote style</h4>

													<blockquote>
														Nam sed enim ac diam condimentum blandit. Nullam mollis justo vitae ligula lobortis ornare ut in mauris.
													</blockquote>
													
													<p>You can create default styled quote with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[blockquote style="quotation-marks"]...[/blockquote]</code>
													
													<h4>Curly brackets quote style</h4>

													<table class="blockquote-curly-brackets">
														<tr><td class="tl"></td><td></td><td class="tr"></td></tr>
														<tr>
															<td class="ml"></td>
															<td class="mm">
																<blockquote>
																	Nam sed enim ac diam condimentum blandit. Nullam mollis justo vitae ligula lobortis ornare ut in mauris.
																</blockquote>
															</td>
															<td class="mr"></td>
														</tr>
														<tr><td class="bl"></td><td></td><td class="br"></td></tr>
													</table>
													
													<p>You can create curled brackets styled quote with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[blockquote style="curly-brackets"]...[/blockquote]</code>
													
													<h4>Quote marks</h4>

													<div class="blockquote-quote-marks">
														<blockquote>
															Nam sed enim ac diam condimentum blandit. Nullam mollis justo vitae ligula lobortis ornare ut in mauris.
														</blockquote>
													</div>
													
													<p>You can create quote marks with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[blockquote style="quote-marks"]...[/blockquote]</code>
													
													<h4>Dashed box quote style</h4>
													
													<blockquote class="blockquote-dashed-box">Nam sed enim ac diam condimentum blandit. Nullam mollis justo vitae ligula lobortis ornare ut in mauris.</blockquote>
													
													<p>You can dashed box quote with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[blockquote style="dashed-box"]...[/blockquote]</code>
]]></content:encoded>

				<title>Spacers</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/spacers/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2011 09:41:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://orange-themes.com/bordeaux/?page_id=274</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3><a href="#">Bordeaux custom spacer styles</a></h3>

													<h4>Default spacer</h4>

													<div class="spacer-default">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create default spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer]</code>
													
													<h4>Star spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-star">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create star spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="star"]</code>
													
													<h4>Dashed spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-dashed">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create dashed spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="dashed"]</code>
													
													<h4>Thick dashed spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-thick-dashed">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create thick dashed spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="thick-dashed"]</code>
													
													<h4>Zig-zag spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-zig-zag">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create zig-zag spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="zig-zag"]</code>
													
													<h4>Yellow ribbon spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-brown-ribbon">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create brown ribbon spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="yellow-ribbon"]</code>
													
													<h4>Red ribbon spacer</h4>
													
													<div class="spacer-red-ribbon">&nbsp;</div>
													
													<p>You can create red ribbon spacer with following shortcode:</p>
													
													<code>[spacer style="red-ribbon"]</code>]]></content:encoded>

				<title>Caption</title>
		<link>http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/caption/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2011 08:53:50 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://bordeaux.orange-themes.com/?page_id=370</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3>Bordeaux Image Caption</h3>
<table class="image-caption aligncenter">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tl"></td>
<td class="tm"></td>
